cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.FL, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with formal specification and synthesis algorithms. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses control flow structures in software systems. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is another possible category as the paper deals with software system construction and reuse of components. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is relevant as the paper discusses Nested-Words Temporal Logic (NWTL) synthesis. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with automated construction of systems from specifications.
